<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَمَّا رَمَاهُ بِهِ مِنْ سَالِفِ التُّهَمِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَقَالَ لِلشَّاءِ خُوضُواْ وَارْتَعُواْ مَعَهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>منْ لاَذَ بِالذِّئْبِ مِنْكُمْ لاَذَ بِالحَرَمِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَإِنْ تُصِبْ أَحَدَاً مِنْكُمْ مخَالِبُهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَإِنَّهَا بَلْسَمٌ يَشْفِي مِنَ السَّقَمِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{شِعْر / محْمُود غُنَيْم}</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>قَلْبُ الأُمّ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>اسْمَعْ نَفَائِسَ مَا يَأْتِيكَ مِنْ حِكَمِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَافْهَمْهُ فَهْمَ لَبِيبٍ نَاقِدٍ وَاعِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>كَانَتْ عَلَى زَعْمِهِمْ فِيمَا مَضَى غَنَمٌ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>بِأَرْضِ بَغْدَادَ يَرْعَى جَمْعَها رَاعِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قَدْ نَامَ عَنهَا فَنَامَتْ غَيرَ وَاحِدَةٍ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لَمْ يَدْعُهَا في الدُّجَي نَحْوَ الْكَرَى دَاعِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَبَيْنَمَا هِيَ وَسْطَ اللَّيْلِ سَاهِرَةٌ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تُحْيِيهِ مَا بَينَ آهَاتٍ وَأَوْجَاعِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>بَدَا لهَا الذِّئْبُ يَسْعَى في الظَّلاَمِ عَلَى<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بُعْدٍ فَصَاحَتْ أَلاَ قُومُواْ إِلى السَّاعِي<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَقَامَ رَاعِي الحِمَى غَضْبَانَ في فَزَعٍ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>